HEADWORD: Helvetic
<hw>Hel*ve"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Helveticus</ets>, fr. <ets>Helvetii</ets> the Helvetii.]</ety>
<def>Of or pertaining to the Helvetii, the ancient inhabitant of the
Alps, now Switzerland, or to the modern states and inhabitant of the
Alpine regions; <as>as, the <ex>Helvetic</ex> confederacy;
<ex>Helvetic</ex> states.</as></def></p>

